title: Ep. - 394 - WELLS ADAMS FROM BACHELOR IN PARADISE
description:
Kate discusses Schumacher and Jack Whitehall: Travels With My Father, both on Netflix.

 

Wells Adams was a contestant on the 12th season of The Bachelorette. He became the bartender on the fourth season of Bachelor in Paradise. This season he serves as a guest host. He discusses this season’s couples, what makes Paradise more hilarious then Bachelor and Bachelorette, and whether the Boom Boom room is ever sanitized.
